{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja monitor template for Spectra LS P5-S01 component functionality feedback. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.20.2 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-20 #}

{# =========================
  P5-S01 Component Functionality Monitor (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: quick live feedback that component-mode routing is actually active/healthy.
  Usage:
    1) Optional refresh actions:
       - spectra_ls.rebuild_registry
       - spectra_ls.validate_contracts
       - spectra_ls.dump_route_trace
    2) Paste/run this in Developer Tools -> Template.
    3) Change pots/encoders/target interactions and watch status/last_attempt update.
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}
{% set s_hosts = 'sensor.shadow_control_hosts' if states['sensor.shadow_control_hosts'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_control_hosts' %}
{% set b_capable = 'binary_sensor.shadow_active_control_capable' if states['binary_sensor.shadow_active_control_capable'] is not none else 'binary_sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_capable' %}

{% set active_target = states(s_target) %}
{% set active_path = states(s_path) %}
{% set control_hosts = states(s_hosts) %}
{% set control_capable = is_state(b_capable, 'on') %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set in_progress = write_controls.in_progress if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.in_progress is defined else false %}
{% set last_attempt = write_controls.last_attempt if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.last_attempt is defined and write_controls.last_attempt is mapping else {} %}
{% set last_status = last_attempt.status if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.status is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set last_reason = last_attempt.reason if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.reason is defined else '' %}
{% set last_corr = last_attempt.correlation_id if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.correlation_id is defined else '' %}
{% set last_ts = last_attempt.timestamp if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.timestamp is defined else '' %}

{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set route_reason = route_trace.reason if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.reason is defined else '' %}

{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined else [] %}

{% set unresolved = state_attr(s_target, 'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set mismatches = state_attr(s_target, 'mismatches') or [] %}

{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{% set write_proof = 'READY' %}
{% if last_status in ['write_applied', 'noop_already_selected'] %}
  {% set write_proof = 'VERIFIED' %}
{% elif last_status is string and last_status.startswith('blocked_') %}
  {% set write_proof = 'BLOCKED' %}
{% endif %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if authority_mode != 'component' %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}
{% if route_decision != 'route_linkplay_tcp' or not contract_valid or (missing_required | length) > 0 %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif (unresolved | length) > 0 or (mismatches | length) > 0 or not fresh or write_proof == 'BLOCKED' %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### P5-S01 Component Functionality Monitor (`spectra_ls`)
- Status: **{{ status }}**
- Write proof: **{{ write_proof }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Is component mode active?
- `write_controls.authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `write_controls.in_progress`: **{{ in_progress }}**

### Last component write feedback
- `last_attempt.status`: **{{ last_status }}**
- `last_attempt.reason`: **{{ last_reason if last_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_attempt.correlation_id`: **{{ last_corr if last_corr != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_attempt.timestamp`: **{{ last_ts if last_ts != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Routing state
- Active target (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ active_target }}**
- Active path (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ active_path }}**
- Control capable (`{{ b_capable }}`): **{{ control_capable }}**
- Control hosts (`{{ s_hosts }}`): **{{ control_hosts }}**
- Route decision/reason: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}** / **{{ route_reason if route_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Contract + parity health
- Contract valid: **{{ contract_valid }}**
- Missing required entities: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- Parity unresolved count: **{{ unresolved | length }}**
- Parity mismatch count: **{{ mismatches | length }}**
- Snapshot freshness (<=300s): **{{ fresh }}** (age_s={{ (age_s | round(1)) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

{% if (missing_required | length) > 0 %}
Missing required entities:
{% for item in missing_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (unresolved | length) > 0 %}
Unresolved parity sources:
{% for item in unresolved %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (mismatches | length) > 0 %}
Parity mismatches:
{% for item in mismatches %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

### Quick interpretation
{% if status == 'PASS' and write_proof == 'VERIFIED' %}
- Component mode is active and a component write has been observed for P5-S01 routing checks.
{% elif status == 'PASS' and write_proof == 'READY' %}
- Component mode is healthy and ready; perform one interaction to verify an applied/no-op write attempt.
{% elif status == 'WARN' and write_proof == 'BLOCKED' %}
- Component mode is partially healthy, but the last write attempt was blocked; inspect `last_attempt.reason` and rerun after stabilization.
{% elif status == 'WARN' %}
- Component path is partially healthy; check authority mode/freshness/parity details above.
{% else %}
- Component path is not healthy for cutover validation yet; resolve FAIL conditions first.
{% endif %}

### Suggested refresh actions
- Service: `spectra_ls.rebuild_registry`
- Service: `spectra_ls.validate_contracts`
- Service: `spectra_ls.dump_route_trace`
